                        <interp inst="t18380402-name-1006" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS VEAR</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I took the prisoner, and have the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I saw a person drop the handkerchief—I picked it up—the gentleman turned round and accused me of picking his pocket—I did not not do it.</p>
